# cqlib CODEOWNERS 文件
# 语法：<文件路径模式>  @<团队或用户名>
# 说明：PR 涉及到对应路径的文件时，GitHub 会自动请求指定的团队或人员进行审核

# ========== 默认规则 ==========
# 所有文件（兜底）由核心维护团队审核
*       @ctq-quantum/core-maintainers

# ========== 核心模块 ==========
# 量子电路核心
/src/cqlib/circuit/           @ctq-quantum/circuit-team
/src/cqlib/circuit/**         @ctq-quantum/circuit-team

# 量子算法
/src/cqlib/algorithms/        @ctq-quantum/algo-team
/src/cqlib/algorithms/**      @ctq-quantum/algo-team

# 模拟器后端
/src/cqlib/simulator/         @ctq-quantum/simulator-team
/src/cqlib/simulator/**       @ctq-quantum/simulator-team

# ========== 文档 ==========
/docs/                        @ctq-quantum/docs-team
/docs/**                      @ctq-quantum/docs-team
README.md                     @ctq-quantum/docs-team
CONTRIBUTING.md               @ctq-quantum/core-maintainers

# ========== 配置与 CI ==========
/.github/                     @ctq-quantum/core-maintainers
/.github/**                   @ctq-quantum/core-maintainers
pyproject.toml                @ctq-quantum/core-maintainers
setup.py                      @ctq-quantum/core-maintainers

# ========== 测试 ==========
/tests/                       @ctq-quantum/core-maintainers
/tests/**                     @ctq-quantum/core-maintainers
